Frequently Asked Questions

Where is the latest BOM (Bill of Materials)?

The latest BOM can be found on GitHub in the BOM folder.

How can I get a Serial # for my finished build?

We are accepting serials over on the Positron 3D Discord. Please submit your request to the #prusawire-serial-request channel over there. There is an example submission and numerous other builds to reference for the format.

Where can I get help with my build?

The community over on the Positron 3D Discord is very helpful. Check out the #prusawire-questions channel there.
